channel.title: Runescape dating
channel.description: Ok so I've seen alot of players who asking ppl out or saying "Looking for bf/gf". And when I play runescape alot of low (and i mean low) level female players saying, "will you be my bf?" or "Your so hot! Will you be mine?" And this form of dating is just stupid :P. But in the end it always seems funny on how they talk. When I was in varrock bank I saw these two level 6, asking out this girl. And the level 6 asks "Are you a play girl?", the female then replies "yeah I am, *wink*." :P I just bursted out laughing. So well reply your thoughts on this.
